quran[5{c,v,t}:
5,37,woh chahain ge ke dozakh ki aag se nikal bhagain magar nah nikal saken ge aur inhen qaim rehne wala azaab diya jaye ga
5,38,"aur chor, khuwa aurat ho ya mard, dono ke haath kaat do, yeh unn ki kamaai ka badla hai aur Allah ki taraf se abrtnak saza Allah ki qudrat sab par ghalib hai aur woh Dana o Beena hai"
5,39,"phir jo zulm karne ke baad tauba kere aur apni islaah kar le to Allah ki nazar inayat phir is par mael ho jaye gi, Allah bohat dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
5,40,"kya tum jantay nahi ho ke Allah zameen aur asmano ki saltanat ka maalik hai? jisay chahay saza day aur jisay chahay maaf kar day, woh har cheez ka ikhtiyar rakhta hai"
5,41,"aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tumahray liye baais ranj nah hon woh log jo kufar ki raah mein barri taiz-gamidikha rahay hain khuwa woh unn mein se hon jo mun se kehte hain hum imaan laaye magar dil unn ke imaan nahi laaye, ya unn mein se hon jo yahodi ban gay hain, jin ka haal yeh hai ke jhoot ke liye kaan lagatay hain, aur dosray logon ki khatir, jo tumahray paas kabhi nahi aeye, sun gun letay phirtay hain, kitaab Allah ke alfaaz ko unn ka sahih mehal mutayyan honay ke bawajood asal maienay se phertey hain, aur logon se kehte hain ke agar tumhe yeh hukum diya jaye to manu nahi to nah manu jisay Allah hi ne fitnah mein daalnay ka iradah kar liya ho to is ko Allah ki girift se bachanay ke liye tum kuch nahi kar saktay, yeh woh log hain jin ke dilon ko Allah ne pak karna nah chaha, un ke liye duniya mein ruswai hai aur akhirat mein sakht saza"
